title: #92Noon Draft Day! Charch/Wobby/Leber/Caplan
description: Charch is in studio for a couple segments to start, then Wobby checks in from Nashville where the draft is taking place, Ben Leber in studio with more takes and opinion, longtime NFL insider Adam Caplan joins on the hotline, and PA empties his notebook on some names he likes for the Vikings in this weekend's draft!
